<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
  <meta charset="utf-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Your Resume Matcher Pro Subscription is Active</title>
  <style>
    body {
      font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
      line-height: 1.6;
      color: #333;
      max-width: 600px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      padding: 20px;
    }
    .header {
      background-color: #2ecc71;
      color: white;
      padding: 20px;
      text-align: center;
      border-radius: 5px 5px 0 0;
    }
    .content {
      padding: 20px;
      border: 1px solid #ddd;
      border-top: none;
      border-radius: 0 0 5px 5px;
    }
    .footer {
      margin-top: 20px;
      text-align: center;
      font-size: 12px;
      color: #777;
    }
    .button {
      display: inline-block;
      background-color: #2ecc71;
      color: white;
      padding: 10px 20px;
      text-decoration: none;
      border-radius: 5px;
      margin-top: 15px;
    }
    .receipt {
      background-color: #f9f9f9;
      padding: 15px;
      border-radius: 5px;
      margin: 20px 0;
    }
    .success-checkmark {
      font-size: 48px;
      color: #2ecc71;
      text-align: center;
      margin: 20px 0;
    }
    .tips {
      border-left: 3px solid #2ecc71;
      padding-left: 15px;
      margin: 20px 0;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="header">
    <h1>Your Subscription is Active</h1>
  </div>
  <div class="content">
    <p>Hi {{name}},</p>
    
    <div class="success-checkmark">✓</div>
    
    <p>Great news! Your Resume Matcher Pro subscription is now active. Thank you for your payment of <strong>{{currency}}{{amount}}</strong>.</p>
    
    <div class="receipt">
      <h3>Payment Receipt</h3>
      <p><strong>Amount:</strong> {{currency}}{{amount}}</p>
      <p><strong>Date:</strong> {{currentDate}}</p>
      <p><strong>Next billing date:</strong> {{nextBillingDate}}</p>
    </div>
    
    <p>You now have full access to all our premium features:</p>
    
    <ul>
      <li>Unlimited job tracking</li>
      <li>Advanced ATS optimization</li>
      <li>All premium resume templates</li>
      <li>Priority email support</li>
      <li>Resume revision history</li>
    </ul>
    
    <div class="tips">
      <h3>Pro Tips to Get Started</h3>
      <ul>
        <li>Update your resume with our ATS optimizer</li>
        <li>Set job alerts to get notified about new opportunities</li>
        <li>Track your applications in the dashboard</li>
        <li>Use our AI tools to improve your cover letters</li>
      </ul>
    </div>
    
    <p>Ready to take your job search to the next level? Click below to go to your dashboard:</p>
    
    <p style="text-align: center;">
      <a href="{{appUrl}}/dashboard" class="button">Go to Dashboard</a>
    </p>
    
    <p>If you have any questions about your subscription or need help with any features, our support team is here to help. Just reply to this email!</p>
    
    <p>Best regards,<br>
    The Resume Matcher Team</p>
  </div>
  <div class="footer">
    <p>© {{currentYear}} Resume Matcher. All rights reserved.</p>
    <p>
      <a href="{{appUrl}}/settings/billing">Manage Subscription</a> |
      <a href="{{appUrl}}/settings">Account Settings</a> |
      <a href="{{appUrl}}/privacy">Privacy Policy</a>
    </p>
  </div>
</body>
</html>